      "Artist": "Svetlin Velinov",
      "TCGplayer Tip": "Faithbound Judge is a great early drop that can block most opposing creatures, which grows extremely well into the late game. Once it has enough counters it effectively turns into a Serra Angel that can come back from the graveyard."
